player.seasonOutlook: Wilson is entering his third season with the Dolphins. The 27-year-old has been productive when given the opportunity in his career. He has scored at least 15 fantasy points in nine of 17 career games in which he received 15 or more touches, but it will be difficult for Wilson to get those touches playing behind De'Von Achane, Raheem Mostert and rookie Jaylen Wright without an injury. Wilson is off the radar in fantasy drafts, even in an explosive Dolphins offense.
